{
    "xsappname": "documentinfoextractor",
    "tenant-mode": "dedicated",
    "scopes": [
      {
        "name": "$XSAPPNAME.User",
        "description": "User scope",
        "grant-as-authority-to-apps": ["$XSAPPNAME"]
      },
      {
        "name": "$XSAPPNAME.Admin",
        "description": "Admin scope",
        "grant-as-authority-to-apps": ["$XSAPPNAME"]
      }
    ],
    "authorities": [
      "$ACCEPT_GRANTED_AUTHORITIES"
    ],
    "oauth2-configuration": {
      "redirect-uris": [
        "https://*.cfapps.eu10.hana.ondemand.com/**"
      ]
    }
  }
  

  /*xsappname:

The name of your application. Replace "documentinfoextractor" with the actual name of your app if different.
tenant-mode:

"dedicated" specifies a single tenant setup.
Use "shared" if your application will be shared across multiple tenants.
Scopes:

Define roles like User and Admin for different access levels.
The grant-as-authority-to-apps property allows granting authority to specific applications.
Authorities:

$ACCEPT_GRANTED_AUTHORITIES ensures users with granted roles can access the application.
OAuth2 Configuration:

The redirect-uris array specifies allowed callback URLs after user authentication.
Replace eu10 with your region if different.
*/